		{
			"id": "chk-p0p1",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "**Phase 0–1**\n\n☑ Concept freeze D1–D12\n☑ Research brief + roadmap\n☑ Free NIM pins + pin log\n☑ Docker smoke\n☑ Pre-reg experiment YAML\n☑ Phase 1 research package",
			"x": 50,
			"y": 850,
			"width": 640,
			"height": 640,
			"color": "4"
		},
		{
			"id": "chk-p2",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "**Phase 2 — Paper organism**\n\n☑ Episode runner + SQLite\n☑ Frozen multi-seed fitness\n☑ Weight checkpoints\n☑ Mutation accept / reject\n☑ Ablation B0/Bw/Bc/Bcw + δ\n☑ Evolve schedule / plateau\n☑ Docker candidate eval\n☑ Hardened Docker\n☑ Schema AST + adversarial tests\n\n☑ **δ success** Bcw ≥ B0+δ\n   (+4.44 · abl_de9d2391b0)",
			"x": 730,
			"y": 850,
			"width": 640,
			"height": 640,
			"color": "3"
		},
		{
			"id": "chk-p3",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "**Phase 3 — Free LLM + critic**\n\n☑ Pins: coder / critic / summarizer\n☑ Critic taxonomy + mutation gate\n☑ Router + session budgets\n☑ Summarizer episode distill\n☑ `seo metrics` rollup\n☑ `seo critic-ab` offline A/B\n☑ Live free-NIM field trial\n☑ Mutation memory (SQL)\n☑ Schema contracts\n\n☑ Soft critic soft_pass\n☑ δ claim under free NIM",
			"x": 1410,
			"y": 850,
			"width": 640,
			"height": 640,
			"color": "2"
		},
		{
			"id": "chk-p4",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "**Phase 4–6 — UI · pop · rails**\n\n**P4** ☑ Observer UI + Run jobs\n☑ Live logs · Watch GIF/video\n\n**P5** ☑ Elite · select · multi-lineage\n☑ Multi-agent Watch · runs export\n☑ Best-of phenotype · diagnose\n\n**P6** ☑ seo doctor\n☑ Safety Bc default (diagnose)\n☑ Soak + reproduce package\n☑ Weights --on-seed experiment\n☑ Seed vs active A/B lab note\n☑ Export diagnose | soak\n\n☐ Multi-hour live soak\n☐ Positive Bw−B0 holdout",
